363
00:23:57,380 --> 00:23:59,910
Allow me to re-introduce myself.

364
00:24:02,370 --> 00:24:04,210
I am one of the Tohtsuki Elite Ten:

365
00:24:06,370 --> 00:24:07,800
the seventh seat,

366
00:24:08,850 --> 00:24:10,760
Isshiki Satoshi.

367
00:24:15,510 --> 00:24:16,300
Now...

368
00:24:17,040 --> 00:24:20,270
I'd like to try <i>your</i> cooking, Souma-kun.

369
00:24:24,100 --> 00:24:30,490
Show me the story you'll create on your plate.

370
00:24:40,410 --> 00:24:43,290
Next time on <i>Shokugeki no Souma</i>,

371
00:24:43,290 --> 00:24:45,250
the fifth dish:

372
00:24:46,520 --> 00:24:49,000
The Ice Queen and the Spring Storm.

